data.title: Where To Use
data.text:
You can redeem the MAP Gift Voucher (paper & digital) at the following stores. Click the logo to see the store location of each brand.

Use MAP e-Gift Voucher with MAPClub app. Show the barcode/QR code on the app upon payment at the cashier.

Note: MAP e-Gift Voucher CANNOT be redeemed at Domino's Pizza.
